headline: Here's what top C-suites are saying about tariffs
summary: US President Trump's tariff policies have created a challenging environment for business leaders. Here's what some executives are saying about navigating tariffs, including CEOs from Coca-Cola (KO), Starbucks (SBUX), and AstraZeneca (AZN), and top executives at Meta (META), General Motors (GM), and Amazon (AMZN).
